              "type": "heading",
              "value": "GamesCom, It's Not All Hard Work"
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "Contrary to popular belief, videogame developers are human beings and need some time to socialise, relax and generally not think about videogames for a few hours."
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "As the sun set and the temperature cooled to a bearable level, Hello Games would descend upon the balmy streets of Cologne to eat, drink, dance and be quite obviously British."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
